Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.59,0:00:17.94,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop my love for you
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.59,0:00:17.94,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fscy80\fscx120}{\pos(478,455)}{\fn4YEOVAL}A
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.09,0:00:27.74,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此所谈到的未来  就是有你陪伴的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.27,0:00:31.37,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh baby I can't stop my love for you
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.27,0:00:31.37,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fscy80\fscx120}{\pos(519,455)}{\fn4YEOVAL}A
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.52,0:00:35.04,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愿意成为妳的一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.73,0:00:43.26,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坚信彼此牵在一起的双手  发誓就这样走下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.32,0:00:50.06,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"我讨厌你"这句话  即使是玩笑话我也不忍出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.08,0:00:57.11,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但"我喜欢你"这句话 如果不是事实我也不会说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.84,0:01:05.32,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像妳在无法见面时 没有心思顾及其它一般
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.55,0:01:11.04,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这颗心  只属于一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.64,0:01:15.04,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop my love for you
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.64,0:01:15.04,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fscy80\fscx120}{\pos(478,455)}{\fn4YEOVAL}A
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.19,0:01:24.59,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了不让我俩的爱分隔两地  请你紧紧拥抱住我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.45,0:01:31.73,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如胶似漆  心绪不宁的夜晚仍会造访
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.75,0:01:39.52,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了那时 就更紧地 抱紧彼此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.26,0:22:40.95,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个星空如此闪耀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.85,0:22:50.13,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些无论怎样都是因为有了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.53,0:23:00.51,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若没有了你 我一个人是做不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.04,0:23:11.02,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,映在眼睛里的东西 全都开始倾斜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.17,0:23:21.90,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仰望辽阔的天空 星星多么闪耀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.06,0:23:32.46,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手触不及星星 为何天空如此遥远
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.65,0:23:37.71,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要与你相逢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.85,0:00:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉近最喜欢与最讨厌的距离
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.95,0:00:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人的推理与悬案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.65,0:00:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无人岛以及深海里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.15,0:00:08.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南和平次的推理爆发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.35,0:00:09.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.86,0:00:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外表看似小孩 头脑却异于常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.76,0:00:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字就是 名侦探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.25,0:01:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了参加电视台办的东西部侦探推理大赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.25,0:01:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们和服部平次来到了冲绳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.56,0:01:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无名岛据说发现过无名尸以及奇妙文字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.46,0:01:56.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们和电视台的人一起去无人岛检查场地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.06,0:01:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.06,0:02:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电视台的职员平良伊江小姐遇害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.87,0:02:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尸体旁留下了匪夷所思的讯息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.57,0:02:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且来时的船以及船长亦随之消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.65,0:02:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤岛的公主与龙宫城(追求篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.15,0:02:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 船锚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.96,0:02:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平良小姐潜水的那片海底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.16,0:02:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的有这种东西吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.56,0:02:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锚链断了 上头遍体鳞伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.97,0:02:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.97,0:02:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会是一年前死者所遗的船锚呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.07,0:02:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.37,0:02:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人坐船到这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.17,0:02:42.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这幢房子躲避台风
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.08,0:02:46.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果船锚断了 船漂走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.65,0:02:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.25,0:02:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锚链上沾满了贝壳和海藻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.05,0:02:55.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在海里的样子应该有四、五年了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.35,0:02:56.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四、五年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.06,0:02:59.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像就是那件事情发生的时候吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.76,0:03:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,町长家里连续发生事件的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.06,0:03:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 出了什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.97,0:03:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次是五年前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.97,0:03:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,町长的独生女都小姐被绑架了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.37,0:03:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后一年以后 强盗集团光临了町长的家里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.88,0:03:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,町长的传家之宝金色屏风被抢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.55,0:03:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,町长 该家管家和犯人通过电话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.65,0:03:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说那些绑架犯和抢劫犯似乎是同伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.46,0:03:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来呢 那些犯人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.16,0:03:39.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赎回女儿以及屏风的钱町长都没有付
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.26,0:03:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么不了了之了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.67,0:03:43.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说小姐跟屏风都失踪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.37,0:03:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,町长还真不容易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.57,0:03:51.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事件发生的时候 他的妻子刚刚去世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.48,0:03:54.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个女仆被强盗团伙杀害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.35,0:03:57.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管家也吓得提出辞呈了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.55,0:03:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,町长因为没有付钱赎人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.85,0:04:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被说成是冷血动物而倍受谴责
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.86,0:04:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,町长后来在岛上又发现饿死的无名尸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.26,0:04:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那根柱子上的奇怪文字后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.56,0:04:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上这回的杀人事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.57,0:04:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人觉得他是不是被古索的使者附身了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.67,0:04:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得刻在柱子上的文字是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.98,0:04:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主沉睡之处是"甲"而非"乙"是不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.25,0:04:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个公主是不是指被绑架的小姐呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.06,0:04:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说 那个小姐已经被杀害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.36,0:04:41.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被埋在这岛上的什么地方了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.36,0:04:45.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 她变成了异世界的使者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.86,0:04:47.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加害了平良小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.87,0:04:52.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕异世界之使者的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.87,0:04:54.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用这把刀吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.28,0:05:00.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据古老传说 女性为了防止魂魄被吸走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.85,0:05:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就咬着小刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.85,0:05:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也可以用来防身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.76,0:05:14.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是有趣的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.06,0:05:18.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看这个茶碗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.06,0:05:21.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被谁当烟灰缸用过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.37,0:05:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面有好几种烟头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.27,0:05:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且碗里灭火用的水还没有完全干
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.88,0:05:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换言之 在我们之前有人来过这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.25,0:05:35.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有群来路不明的人在这里聚集过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.45,0:05:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了什么事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.85,0:05:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能不只一两个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.45,0:05:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了一个女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.26,0:05:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正潜藏在这座小岛上的某处吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.76,0:05:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自称"古索使者"的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.26,0:05:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 胡说八道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.26,0:05:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀害平良小姐的犯人的同伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.37,0:05:56.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的就在这座小岛上吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.37,0:06:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这只是推测
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.27,0:06:04.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好正在伺机攻击我们也不一定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.38,0:06:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取走我们所有人的灵魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.55,0:06:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.95,0:06:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来  他们会不会已经埋伏在这屋子里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.45,0:06:14.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.85,0:06:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们除了这里没有别人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.36,0:06:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这房子的玻璃碎了不少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.46,0:06:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁我们谈话的时候 悄悄潜入这里也是很容易的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.07,0:06:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我们分头再仔细地搜查一次吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.07,0:06:32.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.57,0:06:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里害怕地等着也无济于事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.87,0:06:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 久米先生 池间先生 大东先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.21,0:06:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二楼就拜托你们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.05,0:06:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至于我们就和竹富先生在一楼逛逛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.05,0:06:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.95,0:06:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.65,0:06:50.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你一个男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.26,0:06:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事的话挺危险的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.16,0:06:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.76,0:06:58.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被保护的是你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.27,0:07:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.17,0:07:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会空手道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.47,0:07:04.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.67,0:07:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前在东京大会上赢过冠军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.27,0:07:08.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是合气道二段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.58,0:07:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么全靠你们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.18,0:07:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人来的话就交给我们吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.75,0:07:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位大叔和咱们一起来是正确的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.75,0:07:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 看上去最没用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.26,0:07:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 服部 这是最后的房间了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.60,0:07:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少装模作样的  快点开门吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.67,0:07:39.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是失败了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.18,0:07:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 有人在吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.48,0:07:47.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.45,0:07:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似没有人在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.65,0:07:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.35,0:07:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和其它房间相比 这间房间还真大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.96,0:08:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里可能原来是町长和太太住的房间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.26,0:08:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 町长夫妇的相片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.17,0:08:09.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,町长太太真是漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.57,0:08:13.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么 平次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.67,0:08:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么装了两张照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.95,0:08:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这张是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.35,0:08:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,町长和年轻女性的照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.75,0:08:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道这个町长有外遇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.95,0:08:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.76,0:08:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是町长的独生女都小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.16,0:08:36.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长得很像町长太太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.36,0:08:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮肤白皙 个性温柔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.16,0:08:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以大家都在猜想她会嫁给谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.47,0:08:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是任何人也想不到五年前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.07,0:08:46.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在上大学的时候被绑架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.67,0:08:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从此下落不明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.78,0:08:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得你是从九州岛电视台过来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.55,0:08:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么对这件事情这么清楚呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.35,0:09:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在町长家作女佣的松元嘉子是我的表妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.66,0:09:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她经常跟我说这些事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.16,0:09:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个女佣是不是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.86,0:09:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抢劫时遇害的那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.47,0:09:14.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.57,0:09:16.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四年前的那次事件里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.57,0:09:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被强盗集团的其中一人杀害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.67,0:09:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起表兄妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.37,0:09:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,池间先生的母亲以及町长太太是姊妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.58,0:09:27.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐则是他的表亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.45,0:09:31.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这张照片上的城堡没有见过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.15,0:09:33.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在哪里的建筑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.15,0:09:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是城堡 是町长的家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.36,0:09:38.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常豪华的房屋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.36,0:09:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听嘉子说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.36,0:09:46.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房子盖好后 当时还很小的都小姐也很高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.07,0:09:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是城堡里的公主一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.67,0:09:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城堡的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.17,0:09:52.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.17,0:09:57.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那根柱子上刻的公主果然是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.28,0:09:58.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指都小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.98,0:10:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这根柱子上也刻了奇怪的文字呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.05,0:10:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这应该是那位小姐写的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.55,0:10:09.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧 有三处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.66,0:10:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确是用蜡笔写上去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.36,0:10:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最上面的是"千代哥哥"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.37,0:10:22.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下方二十公分处是写"妈咪"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.87,0:10:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最下面是"我"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.27,0:10:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"我"附近有许多条横线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.18,0:10:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来应该是小姐小时候比身高用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.95,0:10:37.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是身高啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.05,0:10:39.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是男孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.55,0:10:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过"妈咪"指的是母亲吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.25,0:10:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐为什么没用敬语
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.56,0:10:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 "妈咪"好像不是指母亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.76,0:10:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看这里 虽然有点淡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.36,0:10:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个房间的门上也用蜡笔写了字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.37,0:10:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈的房间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.77,0:10:58.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.37,0:11:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么是谁呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.88,0:11:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个"妈咪"和"千代哥哥"是谁呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.98,0:11:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会是小姐的同学呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.25,0:11:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.55,0:11:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐还那么小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.05,0:11:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会有那么高的同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.75,0:11:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.36,0:11:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边的门也写着"妈咪"和"千代哥哥"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.06,0:11:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果说那边是"千代哥哥"的房间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.66,0:11:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这间就是"妈咪"的房间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.97,0:11:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不光如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.47,0:11:30.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文字旁边还有奇怪的画
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.27,0:11:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"妈咪"的旁边是鸟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.57,0:11:36.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"千代哥哥"的旁边好像是鳗鱼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.38,0:11:40.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 在这么昏暗的地方看小孩子的画
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.15,0:11:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是恐怖啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.65,0:11:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 无人岛上有这样的房间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.75,0:11:50.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就说明了"妈咪"和"千代哥哥"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.19,0:11:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是和小姐常来这一带的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.56,0:11:57.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 只有等救援来了 再救我们回岛上后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.66,0:12:01.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再问问町长 这两个人是谁吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.87,0:12:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能和这杀人事件有关联
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.17,0:12:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.78,0:12:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁在叫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.98,0:12:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是久米先生吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.58,0:12:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二楼是不是出事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.55,0:12:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说犯人是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.35,0:12:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.56,0:12:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 出了什么事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.16,0:12:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人出现了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.56,0:12:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.97,0:12:36.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小子突然大叫然后跌倒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.37,0:12:41.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自看到了墙上吊着的那幅画以后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.28,0:12:46.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那幅画是都小姐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.65,0:12:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的耶 跟刚才的照片一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.15,0:12:53.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那应该是太太画的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.55,0:12:58.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听嘉子说太太擅长绘画
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.76,0:12:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.96,0:13:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的表妹 町长家的女佣就是她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.37,0:13:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么一来这里和町长家有关系的人有四个了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.97,0:13:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.07,0:13:17.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妈妈是町长太太的妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.38,0:13:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹富和女佣是表兄妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.95,0:13:23.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久米自从国小后跟都小姐一直是同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.45,0:13:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大东先生据说和町长太太从小就认识
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.66,0:13:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从小就认识
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.46,0:13:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年我跟我妈去给町长夫人扫墓的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.36,0:13:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.46,0:13:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妈问他是谁的时候 他说是从小跟太太就认识的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.17,0:13:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妈说不认识你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.87,0:13:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不是真的就不得而知了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.67,0:13:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也不奇怪吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.48,0:13:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你妈跟太太的年龄差远了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.05,0:13:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你妈妈是太太的妹妹的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.55,0:13:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也来过这个岛吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.95,0:14:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.75,0:14:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座岛跟町长家 我之前都没有来过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.16,0:14:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,町长是有钱人 门坎高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.66,0:14:11.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连小姐也只是幼时看过一眼而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.36,0:14:16.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但为什么久米先生看了小姐画会感到惊吓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.27,0:14:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.67,0:14:21.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可能是觉得小姐的灵魂出来了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.57,0:14:25.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为据说小姐已经遇害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.65,0:14:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.05,0:14:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这房子应该是没有藏匿可疑的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.15,0:14:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家集合到楼下的房间里等待救援吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.07,0:14:53.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这未免太久了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.97,0:15:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔八成又在哪跟女郎喝酒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.85,0:15:03.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个白痴大叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.25,0:15:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么声音啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.56,0:15:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难…难道是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.66,0:15:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是救援船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.76,0:15:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.27,0:15:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.27,0:15:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那船有点怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.77,0:15:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有灯亮 停靠的方式也颇奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.76,0:15:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手法真残忍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.86,0:15:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人用水管之类的硬物反复殴打船长后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.47,0:15:57.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎死后还在打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.27,0:15:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.77,0:16:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后把船长挂在船头上再写上那几个字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.08,0:16:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"我乃古索的使者"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.95,0:16:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有恨到极点才会这么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.05,0:16:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 到底是谁呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.65,0:16:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然在这岛上除了我们以外还有其它人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.26,0:16:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在等着杀害我们的杀人狂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.96,0:16:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.76,0:16:27.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这艘船撞到栈桥的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.97,0:16:30.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都在那幢房子里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.37,0:16:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操纵这艘船的犯人应该就在这附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.58,0:16:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自封"古索使者"的犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.65,0:16:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不一定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.45,0:16:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.25,0:16:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才我看了一下船里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.35,0:16:51.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船长座位边有个像是小型电视的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.56,0:16:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了上面的雷达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.86,0:16:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这艘船好像只是一直绕着岛航行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.76,0:17:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 自动驾驶仪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.87,0:17:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这个的话没有人也可以操纵船的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.37,0:17:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 小弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.57,0:17:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海里的潮流也是会有影响的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.27,0:17:12.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能用自动驾驶把船正好开到栈桥这来吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.25,0:17:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 设定仔细就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.95,0:17:22.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自动驾驶会因潮流影响的误差大约是50-100尺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.16,0:17:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果说设置时紧贴着岸边行驶的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.96,0:17:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沿着海岸的珊瑚礁走就可以碰到栈桥了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.97,0:17:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们看 船的侧面有着擦撞的痕迹对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.07,0:17:42.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是擦撞到珊瑚礁行驶的证据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.98,0:17:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换言之 利用自动驾驶 几个小时前把船开出栈桥的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.85,0:17:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个犯罪手法就成立了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.05,0:17:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在岛上的我们也能做到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.75,0:17:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂… 难道说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.06,0:18:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们之中可能藏有犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.06,0:18:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们四个人为了寻找平良小姐离开船时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.57,0:18:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不是说也跟着下船了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.77,0:18:16.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时在船上的最后一个人就可以趁机把船长杀死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.68,0:18:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.38,0:18:21.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.15,0:18:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是最后一个下船的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.35,0:18:27.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…难道是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.15,0:18:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是自我下船后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.16,0:18:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都可以偷偷回去 一样可以行凶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.86,0:18:35.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 你没忘记吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.96,0:18:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侦探小哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.66,0:18:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平良小姐出事的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.77,0:18:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 你不是说了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.97,0:18:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平良小姐旁边的沙滩上写的字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.98,0:18:54.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是大家当时都还在另一头不可能写的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.85,0:18:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那行字是在满潮线的下方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.35,0:19:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不赶在发现平良小姐稍早前到达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.65,0:19:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海浪就会冲走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.26,0:19:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你确实说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.76,0:19:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而…而且 这跟平良小姐、船长出事时写的字一模一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.16,0:19:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说明凶手是同一个人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.57,0:19:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此一来 我们之中就不可能有犯人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.87,0:19:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若犯人不只一个的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.17,0:19:23.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们之中就有可能有共犯 替他写了同样的文字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.18,0:19:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这字也能是犯人设下的陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.85,0:19:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们以为犯人在我们之中  而起内哄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.05,0:19:37.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何 船回来了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.86,0:19:42.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 有什么事回去的话再说吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.36,0:19:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 船长被放下来的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.86,0:19:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看已经没有燃料了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.37,0:19:50.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还不只这些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.87,0:19:52.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无线电也被破坏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.77,0:19:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的行李也都不见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.87,0:19:57.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.88,0:20:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人要把我们困在岛上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.05,0:20:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能还有什么事要做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.65,0:20:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.55,0:20:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要杀人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.25,0:20:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不想被杀的话 最好先待在刚才的房子里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.26,0:20:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着救援前来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.36,0:20:19.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.26,0:20:21.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到什么时候救援船才会来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.87,0:20:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.37,0:20:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 平次 我们也先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.88,0:20:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.08,0:20:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.15,0:20:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工藤  这件案子很奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.75,0:20:40.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初的被害人平良小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.45,0:20:44.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尸体很仔细地放着 手好好地摆放着 眼睛也是闭上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.46,0:20:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是船长却是被殴打致死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.86,0:20:52.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人可能不是同一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.67,0:20:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是这样还是差太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.97,0:20:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我最在意的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.07,0:21:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被杀害前船长跟平良小姐的举动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.78,0:21:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平良小姐特地去有激流的海域潜水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.75,0:21:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船长则是直到预定时间为止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.45,0:21:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在岛上绕来绕去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.35,0:21:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船上的海底探测器也是开着的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.26,0:21:18.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像大家都在找什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.36,0:21:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是我在海底看见的那个船锚的锚链捆住的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.66,0:21:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某样东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.57,0:21:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 工藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.87,0:21:32.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才待的那个房间椅子的背面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.67,0:21:35.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有蜡笔写过的孩子字迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.18,0:21:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我坐的字背面写的是"我"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.58,0:21:41.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兰的椅子是"妈妈"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.95,0:21:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工藤 但我坐的椅子背面是"金城先生"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.85,0:21:49.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是小姐写的字吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.46,0:21:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过金城先生不是她的父亲吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.96,0:21:55.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不写"爸爸"呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.16,0:21:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有写字的椅子只有那三张
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.87,0:22:02.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 都没有和小姐比身高的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.57,0:22:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"妈咪" 和"千代哥哥"的椅子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.97,0:22:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有房间却没有椅子  的确很奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.98,0:22:16.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"妈咪"和"千代哥哥"到底是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.17,0:23:48.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.87,0:23:50.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煎饼和饼干
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.18,0:23:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才 是什么声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.15,0:23:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.25,0:23:57.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是水滴下来的声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.65,0:24:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办 朝这里接近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.96,0:24:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.36,0:24:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"古索的使者"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.96,0:24:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:12.56,0:24:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤岛的公主与龙宫城(解决篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.47,0:24:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NEXT CONAN'S HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.67,0:24:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城堡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.87,0:24:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次终于是解决篇了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.58,0:24:24.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人就是你
